BMix version history file

BMix 1.2

-New option for maximum framerate per output (defaults to unlimited)
-New input relay feature that sends copies of incoming data as it arrives

BMix 1.1 - 20080824

-Added command line argument for verbosity level (-v)
-Added command line argument to disable GUI preview (-d)
-Added ability to consume streams of any maxval 1..255
-Added ability to optionally send heartbeat packets to blproxy
 (heartbeat config is associated with input lines)
-Cleaned up all "println" logging; now using logging framework
-Overall code cleanup and preening


BMix 1.0a - initial release

-Intended to satisfy the basic initial requirements specified by Tim
